candle.exe Sample.wxs   -->   Sample.wixobj   (like a complier)
light.exe Sample.wixobj   -->   Sample.msi    (like a linker)
basic structure:
<Wix>
    <Product>
        <Package>
            <MediaTemplate>
            <Directory Id="TARGETDIR" Name="SourceDir">
            <Icon Id="L.ico" SourceFile="Launcher.exe" />
            <DirectoryRef>
                <Component>
                    <File>
                <Component>
                    <RegistryKey>
            <Feature>
                <ComponentRef>













